<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title><%= @title || 'auth-otp demo' %></title>
    <style>
      :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
      body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
             max-width: 32rem; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; line-height: 1.6; }
      h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      form { margin: 1rem 0; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; }
      label { display: block; margin: 0.5rem 0 0.25rem; font-weight: 600; }
      input[type=email], input[type=text] {
        width: 100%; padding: 0.5rem; font-size: 1rem; box-sizing: border-box;
        border: 1px solid #999; border-radius: 4px;
      }
      button { padding: 0.5rem 1rem; font-size: 1rem; cursor: pointer;
               border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 4px; background: #f5f5f5; }
      button:hover { background: #e8e8e8; }
      .notice { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; background: #eef; border-left: 4px solid #66f;
                border-radius: 4px; margin: 1rem 0; }
      .error { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; background: #fee; border-left: 4px solid #c33;
               border-radius: 4px; margin: 1rem 0; }
      .otp-banner { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; background: #ffd; border-left: 4px solid #cc0;
                    border-radius: 4px; margin: 1rem 0; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; }
      nav { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666; }
      nav a { color: inherit; }
      footer { margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 0.85em; color: #888; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">/</a> &middot; <a href="/login">/login</a>
    </nav>
    <%= yield %>
    <footer>
      auth-otp demo (homura on Cloudflare Workers + D1 + mailpit).
      ローカル開発では OTP を mailpit (<a href="http://127.0.0.1:8025/" target="_blank">http://127.0.0.1:8025/</a>) に送信します。
      mailpit が落ちている場合のみ、開発フォールバックで画面に OTP を表示します。
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
